ablet_extra&quot;],&quot;motion_fx_translateX_affectedRange&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;%&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:100}}}" data-widget_type="image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><picture><source srcset="https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1.avif 335w,https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1-166x300.avif 166w" sizes="(max-width: 335px) 100vw, 335px" type="image/avif"><source srcset="https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1.webp 335w,https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1-166x300.webp 166w" sizes="(max-width: 335px) 100vw, 335px" type="image/webp"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMzUiIGhlaWdodD0iNjA2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzM1IDYwNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgc3R5bGU9ImZpbGw6I2NmZDRkYjtmaWxsLW9wYWNpdHk6IDAuMTsiLz48L3N2Zz4=" data-src="https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1.png" height="606" width="335" data-srcset="https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1.png 335w, https://goxxii.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/trucks-1-166x300.png 166w" data-sizes="(max-width: 335px) 100vw, 335px" class="sp-no-webp attachment-full size-full wp-image-1172 sp-no-webp" alt="three white trucks stickers" loading="lazy" decoding="async"></picture></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0b2fcf5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="0b2fcf5" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6d4ea7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="6d4ea7f" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Your Trusted
<span style="color:#0078ff">Trucking Partners</span></h2></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-3aa3927 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="3aa3927" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p data-start="479" data-end="817">At XXII Century, we support <strong data-start="507" data-end="559">CDL truck drivers in Chicago and across the U.S.</strong> with dependable routes, steady freight, and a professional logistics network. Whether you’re hauling dry van, temperature-controlled freight, intermodal, or full truckload, our asset-based fleet and optimized routing help you stay efficient and on the move.</p><p data-start="819" data-end="1084">We&rsquo;re more than a carrier &mdash; we&rsquo;re a <strong data-start="855" data-end="881">driver-focused partner</strong> built on communication, predictable miles, and on-time freight delivery. Our system is designed to reduce wait times, keep loads consistent, and help drivers get from point A to point B with confidence.</p><p data-start="440" data-end="756">logistics approach is designed to reduce downtime, improve visibility, and move your freight with precision from point A to point B.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-6636c7b centuary-btn-cls elementor-mobile-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="6636c7b" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper"><a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="https://goxxii.com/freight-shipping-services/" target="_blank"><span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"><span class="elementor-button-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-angle-double-right" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M224.3 273l-136 136c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.6-22.6c-9.4-9.4-9.4-2