r" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-31824c9 elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="31824c9" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">GET IN TOUCH
<span style="color:#0078ff">WITH US!</span></h2></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-2e845dc elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="2e845dc" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>Let us know how we can help. We&rsquo;d love to hear from you.</p></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7d46975 centuary-btn-cls elementor-align-center elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="7d46975" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper"><a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="tel:630-948-0501"><span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"><span class="elementor-button-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-angle-double-right" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M224.3 273l-136 136c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.6-22.6c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l96.4-96.4-96.4-96.4c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9L54.3 103c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0l136 136c9.5 9.4 9.5 24.6.1 34zm192-34l-136-136c-9.4-9.4-24.6-9.4-33.9 0l-22.6 22.6c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9l96.4 96.4-96.4 96.4c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9l22.6 22.6c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0l136-136c9.4-9.2 9.4-24.4 0-33.8z"></path></svg></span><span class="elementor-button-text">call Now</span></span></a></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0656fd6 centuary-btn-cls call-btn-cls elementor-align-center elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-button" data-id="0656fd6" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="button.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-button-wrapper"><a class="elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm" href="mailto:hr@goxxii.com"><span class="elementor-button-content-wrapper"><span class="elementor-button-icon"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-angle-double-right" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M224.3 273l-136 136c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.6-22.6c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l96.4-96.4-96.4-96.4c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9L54.3 103c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0l136 136c9.5 9.4 9.5 24.6.1 34zm192-34l-136-136c-9.4-9.4-24.6-9.4-33.9 0l-22.6 22.6c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9l96.4 96.4-96.4 96.4c-9.4 9.4-9.4 24.6 0 33.9l22.6 22.6c9.4 9.4 24.6 9.4 33.9 0l136-136c9.4-9.2 9.4-24.4 0-33.8z"></path></svg></span><span class="elementor-button-text">email us</span></span></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-22e6299 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="22e6299" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="e-con-inner"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-f2323ea e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f2323ea" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d4f8fd8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="d4f8fd8" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9190316 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="9190316" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><h3 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Top Questions from Owner Operators Considering XXII Century</h3></div></div><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-336426e elementor-widget elementor-widget-n-accordion" data-id="336426e" data-element_type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;max_items_expended&quot;:&quot;multiple&quot;,&quot;default_state&quot;:&quot;all_collapsed&quot;,&quot;n_accordion_animation_duration&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;ms&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:400,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="nested-accordion.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="e-n-accordion" aria-label="Accordion. Open links with Enter or Space, close with Escape, and navigate with Arrow Keys"><details id="e-n-accordion-item-5380" class="e-n-accordion-item"><summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="1" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-5380"><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><span class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text">What types of truck driving jobs are available? </span></span><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'><span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-up" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M240.971 130.524l194.343 194.343c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941l-22.667 22.667c-9.357 9.357-24.522 9.375-33.901.04L224 227.495 69.255 381.516c-9.379 9.335-24.544 9.317-33.901-.04l-22.667-22.667c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941L207.03 130.525c9.372-9.373 24.568-9.373 33.941-.001z"></path></svg></span><span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-down" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z"></path></svg></span></span></summary><div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-5380" class="elementor-element elementor-element-f98a16b e-con-full hl-faq-child-panel e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f98a16b" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-33d60bf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="33d60bf" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p data-start="559" data-end="1017">We offer a variety of opportunities for both <a href="https://goxxii.com/owner-operators/"><strong data-start="604" data-end="623">owner operators</strong></a> and <a href="https://goxxii.com/company-drivers/"><strong data-start="628" data-end="651">company CDL drivers</strong></a>, including local, regional, and over-the-road (OTR) positions. If you’re searching for <strong data-start="739" data-end="768">local owner operator jobs</strong>, we provide dedicated routes that offer consistent home time and steady freight. For drivers interested in long-haul or regional work, our <strong data-start="908" data-end="934">dry van owner operator</strong> and company dry-van positions deliver reliable miles and strong earning potential.</p><p data-start="1019" data-end="1260">Whether you&rsquo;re an experienced <strong data-start="1049" data-end="1076">owner operator trucking</strong> professional or a company driver looking for the next step in your career, we make sure you have access to quality freight, competitive pay, and a supportive team to help you succeed.</p></div></div></div></details><details id="e-n-accordion-item-5381" class="e-n-accordion-item"><summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="2" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-5381"><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><span class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text">How do I apply for a driving position? </span></span><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'><span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-up" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M240.971 130.524l194.343 194.343c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941l-22.667 22.667c-9.357 9.357-24.522 9.375-33.901.04L224 227.495 69.255 381.516c-9.379 9.335-24.544 9.317-33.901-.04l-22.667-22.667c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941L207.03 130.525c9.372-9.373 24.568-9.373 33.941-.001z"></path></svg></span><span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-down" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z"></path></svg></span></span></summary><div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-5381" class="elementor-element elementor-element-df57ae2 e-con-full hl-faq-child-panel e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="df57ae2" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-642f451 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="642f451" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p data-start="1314" data-end="1678">Applying is fast and straightforward. You can <a href="https://intelliapp.driverapponline.com/c/goxxii?r=Eve&amp;uri_b=ia_goxxii_1118549354" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong data-start="1360" data-end="1376">apply online</strong></a> through our secure application, or <a href="tel:630-948-0501"><strong data-start="1412" data-end="1447">speak directly with a recruiter</strong></a> if you prefer a personal conversation. Our team is available to answer questions about pay, routes, home time, equipment requirements, and details like <strong data-start="1600" data-end="1639">owner operator semi truck insurance</strong>, onboarding, and settlement schedules. Once you submit your application, our staff will walk you through every step of the hiring and onboarding process. We keep things simple and transparent so you can get approved and start running loads as quickly as possible.</p></div></div></div></details><details id="e-n-accordion-item-5382" class="e-n-accordion-item"><summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="3" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-5382"><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><span class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text">How soon can I start driving after applying? </span></span><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'><span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-up" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M240.971 130.524l194.343 194.343c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941l-22.667 22.667c-9.357 9.357-24.522 9.375-33.901.04L224 227.495 69.255 381.516c-9.379 9.335-24.544 9.317-33.901-.04l-22.667-22.667c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941L207.03 130.525c9.372-9.373 24.568-9.373 33.941-.001z"></path></svg></span><span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-down" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z"></path></svg></span></span></summary><div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-5382" class="elementor-element elementor-element-1f09b94 e-con-full hl-faq-child-panel e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="1f09b94" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-1eee5cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="1eee5cc" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p data-start="1964" data-end="2247">Most qualified drivers can start driving <strong data-start="2005" data-end="2031">within just a few days</strong> after applying. After your application is reviewed, we quickly complete onboarding, verify documentation, assist with any required <strong data-start="2163" data-end="2202">owner operator semi truck insurance</strong> information, and finalize your driver file.</p><p data-start="2249" data-end="2531">As soon as you&rsquo;re cleared, you&rsquo;ll be dispatched with your first load &mdash; whether you&rsquo;re beginning with local work, regional lanes, or joining our reefer or <strong data-start="2393" data-end="2419">dry van owner operator</strong> fleet. We know drivers are eager to get on the road, so our priority is to get you earning as soon as possible.</p></div></div></div></details><details id="e-n-accordion-item-5383" class="e-n-accordion-item"><summary class="e-n-accordion-item-title" data-accordion-index="4" tabindex="-1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e-n-accordion-item-5383"><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><span class="e-n-accordion-item-title-text">Why should I choose XXII Century as an owner operator? </span></span><span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'><span class='e-opened'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-up" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M240.971 130.524l194.343 194.343c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941l-22.667 22.667c-9.357 9.357-24.522 9.375-33.901.04L224 227.495 69.255 381.516c-9.379 9.335-24.544 9.317-33.901-.04l-22.667-22.667c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941L207.03 130.525c9.372-9.373 24.568-9.373 33.941-.001z"></path></svg></span><span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden="true" class="e-font-icon-svg e-fas-chevron-down" viewbox="0 0 448 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M207.029 381.476L12.686 187.132c-9.373-9.373-9.373-24.569 0-33.941l22.667-22.667c9.357-9.357 24.522-9.375 33.901-.04L224 284.505l154.745-154.021c9.379-9.335 24.544-9.317 33.901.04l22.667 22.667c9.373 9.373 9.373 24.569 0 33.941L240.971 381.476c-9.373 9.372-24.569 9.372-33.942 0z"></path></svg></span></span></summary><div role="region" aria-labelledby="e-n-accordion-item-5383" class="elementor-element elementor-element-f9b8a1f e-con-full hl-faq-child-panel e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="f9b8a1f" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-af03a89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="af03a89" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><p>At XXII Century, we know that owner operators value independence and steady income. That&rsquo;s why we focus on providing what matters most: <strong data-start="2355" data-end="2452">consistent freight, weekly settlements, no forced dispatch, and a fair trailer-to-truck ratio</strong> to minimize downtime. You’ll have the freedom to run your business the way you want while having access to the support, tools, and resources of a larger company. We offer reliable freight partnerships that keep you moving, flexible options that allow you to choose the loads that fit your goals, and a dedicated support team to help with logistics and compliance. With us, you’ll never feel like just another number — we treat our owner operators as true business partners.</p></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><footer 7 data-elementor-type="footer" data-elementor-id="897" class="elementor elementor-897 elementor-location-footer" data-elementor-post-type="elementor_library"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-d94bbc5 footer-cls e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="d94bbc5" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}"><div class="e-con-inner"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-169f8e5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="169f8e5" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-ab086cc e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="ab086cc" data-element_type="container"><div class="elementor-element elementor-element-9459c05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="9459c05" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><a href="https://goxxii.com"><img data-lazyloaded="1" src="data: